      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line for my brand and i really want to make sure we get the vibe right. i want to capture that \"authentic urban\" aesthetic without it feeling like we're just playing dress up or being appropriative. can you describe what defines that urban look? like, what are the core elements that make it feel real and rooted in the culture?",
