      "content": "The \"authentic urban\" look is really about reflecting the real life of the city, which is often defined by a certain kind of grit and resilience. It's less about trendy clothes and more about functional, durable pieces that can handle the concrete jungle. You'll see influences from working-class culture, sportswear, and a certain unpolished, lived-in feel that speaks to the streets.",
