      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"grit and resilience\" thing makes sense. When you're talking about that \"lived-in feel\" and the \"streets,\" what specific communities or groups are usually at the heart of that? Like, if I'm looking for the specific inspiration for the silhouettes and colors, which demographics should I be looking at to make sure it feels grounded in the actual culture?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
